# Genii Studio - CLI Agent Context
# Load this when using Claude Code, Codex, Kimi, or OpenCode

## Project
Factory-built housing development pipeline. AI generates CAD/BIM plans from address/APN.

## Tech Stack
- FreeCAD 1.1.1 (CAD/BIM)
- Python 3.12 + bundled FreeCAD interpreter
- ERPNext v16 (project management)
- GitHub (version control + plan publishing)
- PM2 (agent orchestration)

## Key Files
- macros/FullPipeline.py - Main orchestrator
- macros/GenerateSitePlan.py - Address → CAD
- macros/FloorPlanGenerator.py - Architectural plans
- macros/ComplianceEngine.py - HCD/Title24/CALGreen checks
- macros/ERPNext_Integration.py - Auto-project creation
- agents/pm2.config.js - 10-agent deployment

## Business Rules
- SIP walls 6.5" thick, roofs 8.25" thick
- 14-gauge C-channel steel subfloors
- HCD SHL 620 / Title 24 CF1R / CALGreen compliance required
- All plans published to GitHub with Git LFS
- ERPNext project auto-created per development

## FreeCAD Execution
Use: /Applications/FreeCAD.app/Contents/Resources/bin/python
With: PYTHONPATH=/Applications/FreeCAD.app/Contents/Resources/lib
